body:
@pengjiang030 we proposed a [PR ](https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/pull/5919)to enable DDP-CPU, would you like to have a try with this new interface on CPU side?
DDP-CPU code: https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/blob/master/torch/nn/parallel/distributed_cpu.py 
BTW, the DDP-CPU interface is more simple then the DDP on GPU.
